         base-files (>= 3.1.10)
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Description: NSS module for Link-local Multicast Name Resolution
 nss-llmnr is a plugin for the GNU Name Service Switch (NSS) functionality
 of the GNU C Library (glibc) providing host name resolution via Link-Local
 Multicast Name Resolution, effectively allowing name resolution by common
 Unix/Linux programs to modern Windows systems.
